BEGIN_PGML Read the scenario. Then write a complete sentence that defines a variable to use. Lastly, write an equation to model the scenario. There is no need to solve the equation.
[$name] puts a pot of water from the tap onto the stove and turns the burner all the way up. The water temperature starts at [`[$initial]\,^{\circ}F`] and climbs steadily up to the boiling point of [`[$final]\,^{\circ}F\text{,}`] raising at a rate of [`[$rate]\,\frac{^{\circ}F}{\text{min}}\text{.}`] How long will it take for the pot to boil? Write an equation to model this scenario. There is no need to solve it.
